"title": "8242: ethics, personal",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8242: ethics, personal",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture teaches that individuals have a responsibility before God for their conduct.</p>\n<h2>Ethical principles in relationships generally</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:12\">MAT 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:39\">MAT 22:39</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:31\">MRK 12:31</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:13-Exod20:17\">EXO 20:13–20:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:17-Deut5:21\">DEU 5:17–5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:18\">LEV 19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:31\">LUK 6:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:9-Rom12:10\">ROM 12:9–12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:10\">GAL 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:10\">1TI 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:8\">1PE 3:8</a></p>\n<h2>The importance of thoughts and motives</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:1-Matt6:4\">MAT 6:1–6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:13-Exod21:14\">EXO 21:13–21:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:22\">MAT 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:28\">MAT 5:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:8\">PHP 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:15\">JAS 1:15</a></p>\n<h2>Personal ethics in relation to God</h2>\n<h3>Idolatry prohibited</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:4\">EXO 20:4</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:8\">DEU 5:8</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:1\">LEV 26:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:14\">JOS 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:15\">ACT 14:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:21\">1JN 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:9\">REV 22:9</a></p>\n<h3>God's name to be honoured</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:7\">EXO 20:7</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:11\">DEU 5:11</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:12\">LEV 19:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:58\">DEU 28:58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:34\">MAT 5:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:9\">MAT 6:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:2\">LUK 11:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:12\">JAS 5:12</a></p>\n<h3>Sabbath observance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:8\">EXO 20:8</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:12\">DEU 5:12</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:15\">EXO 31:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:21\">EXO 34:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:2\">LEV 26:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:31\">NEH 10:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:2\">ISA 56:2</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience to God's commands</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:29\">ACT 5:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:16\">DEU 26:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21\">MAT 7:21</a></p>\n<h2>Personal ethics and human relationships</h2>\n<h3>Wives and husbands</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:22\">EPH 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25\">EPH 5:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:24\">GEN 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:5\">DEU 24:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:6\">MAT 19:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:9\">MRK 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:10-1Cor7:11\">1CO 7:10–7:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:18-Col3:19\">COL 3:18–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:1\">1PE 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:7\">1PE 3:7</a></p>\n<h3>Children and parents</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:1-Eph6:4\">EPH 6:1–6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:12\">EXO 20:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:15\">EXO 21:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:9\">LEV 20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:7\">DEU 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:18\">PRO 19:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:6\">PRO 22:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:22\">PRO 23:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:20-Col3:21\">COL 3:20–3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:4\">1TI 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:4\">1TI 5:4</a></p>\n<h3>The extended family</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:8\">1TI 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:10\">LEV 25:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:25\">LEV 25:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:49\">LEV 25:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num36:8\">NUM 36:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:5\">DEU 25:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:29\">1SA 20:29</a></p>\n<h3>Slaves and masters</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:22\">COL 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:1\">COL 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:2\">EXO 21:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:5\">EPH 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:9\">EPH 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:1\">1TI 6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:9\">TIT 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:18\">1PE 2:18</a></p>\n<h3>Employers and employees</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:13\">LEV 19:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:14-Deut24:15\">DEU 24:14–24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:13-Job31:14\">JOB 31:13–31:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:13\">JER 22:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">MAL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:4\">JAS 5:4</a></p>",
